20:21.154 --> 20:23.389
Just help me start off
on the right foot with her.

20:23.422 --> 20:25.491
You know, what does
she like to eat?

20:25.524 --> 20:26.559
Does she like wine?

20:26.592 --> 20:28.028
Should I bring flowers?

20:28.061 --> 20:30.462
