20:30.496 --> 20:32.364
daisies.

20:32.398 --> 20:34.466
She loves daisies.

20:43.043 --> 20:44.878
- Hey!
- Hey.

20:44.911 --> 20:48.882
They're beautiful,
but I'm, uh, actually allergic.

20:48.915 --> 20:50.050
Oh.

20:53.687 --> 20:54.855
Come in.

20:54.888 --> 20:55.922
Yeah.

20:58.859 --> 21:01.460
So, is, uh, JJ
joinin' us for dinner?

21:01.493 --> 21:02.696
No, he, uh, he ate dinner.

21:02.729 --> 21:04.764
He's in his room
watching the game.

21:04.798 --> 21:06.532
Oh, right.

21:06.565 --> 21:08.001
He a big Sox fan?

21:08.034 --> 21:09.002
Oh, of course!

21:09.035 --> 21:12.105
I indoctrinated
him very early.

21:12.138 --> 21:13.807
Yeah, my mom too.

21:13.840 --> 21:15.675
She used to always
take me to Fenway.

21:15.709 --> 21:18.178
Oh, JJ's been dying to go.

21:18.211 --> 21:20.046
It's just things have been
a bit tight this year.

21:20.080 --> 21:22.616
Oh, well, I totally get that.

21:22.649 --> 21:26.552
My mom, I mean,
she just never paid the bills.

21:26.585 --> 21:28.520
I'm actually in the middle
of getting my Psy-D.

21:28.554 --> 21:30.589
- Oh, so you're in school?
- Post-doc.

21:30.624 --> 21:31.858
It's been amazing,
I get to see clients,

21:31.892 --> 21:33.960
I just don't get paid yet.

21:33.994 --> 21:36.428
I'm also finishing off
my dissertation, so.

21:36.462 --> 21:37.864
And bein' a mom.

21:37.898 --> 21:40.867
Oh, that part, I really love.

21:40.901 --> 21:42.802
So you wanna be a therapist?

21:42.836 --> 21:45.772
Yeah, family counselor.

21:45.805 --> 21:49.441
I can see that.

21:49.475 --> 21:52.612
So, uh, what kind of
law do you practice?

21:52.646 --> 21:54.180
Corporate.

21:54.214 --> 21:57.150
Yeah, mostly contracts,

21:57.183 --> 22:00.020
financial transactions,
regulatory compliance,

22:00.053 --> 22:01.087
nothin' sexy.

22:01.121 --> 22:02.322
Big companies?

22:02.355 --> 22:06.458
Yeah, yeah, we mostly just try
to protect them from themselves.

22:06.492 --> 22:09.095
And from the little people
they screw over?

22:09.129 --> 22:10.529
Well, I don't know about that.

22:10.562 --> 22:12.165
Your mom must be so proud.

22:16.568 --> 22:18.705
- I'm joking!
- Oh.

22:18.738 --> 22:21.473
No, seriously, though,
she must be thrilled!

22:21.507 --> 22:24.476
You've done very
well for yourself.

22:24.510 --> 22:25.712
Thanks.

22:25.745 --> 22:27.948
You're only a little evil.

22:27.981 --> 22:29.616
Aren't we all?

22:29.649 --> 22:30.516
I guess.

22:30.549 --> 22:31.550
Yes.

22:33.186 --> 22:36.189
So you and your mom
must be very close.

22:36.222 --> 22:37.924
Yeah, she's great.

22:37.958 --> 22:39.626
I mean, she raised me
all by herself.

22:39.659 --> 22:40.827
- Mm.
- Come on, that's bullshit!

22:40.860 --> 22:41.995
Hey, JJ!

22:42.028 --> 22:43.229
Language!

22:43.263 --> 22:44.831
Ugh, the Yankees hit a granny.

22:44.864 --> 22:47.834
Fuck!

22:47.867 --> 22:49.903
So I checked out
this vegetarian place.

22:49.936 --> 22:51.071
It's got great reviews.

22:51.104 --> 22:52.806
Yeah? You vegetarian?

22:52.839 --> 22:55.075
No, no, but I dabble.

22:55.108 --> 22:56.643
You?

22:56.676 --> 22:58.678
Pretty far from it.

22:58.712 --> 23:00.080
No shit.

23:06.152 --> 23:07.687
Oh, you know what?

23:07.721 --> 23:10.790
I forgot about the wine.

23:10.824 --> 23:13.059
Would you like to see
how it pairs with this

23:13.093 --> 23:14.928
delectable mess?

23:14.961 --> 23:18.631
I'm good with water,
but you go ahead.

23:18.665 --> 23:20.133
- Oh, you don't like the wine?
- No, I love wine,

23:20.166 --> 23:22.002
I just don't drink anymore.

23:22.035 --> 23:23.803
Oh, I'm sorry,
I didn't realize.

23:23.837 --> 23:27.807
No, it's fine! Seriously.

23:27.841 --> 23:29.142
How long?

23:29.175 --> 23:31.011
Since JJ was in my belly.

23:33.579 --> 23:34.748
That's amazing.

23:34.781 --> 23:36.049
It's survival.

23:39.019 --> 23:40.586
My mom was into pills.

23:43.089 --> 23:44.891
Oh, I'm sorry.

23:44.924 --> 23:46.726
Nah, she's much better now.

23:49.696 --> 23:51.164
I'm glad to hear,

23:51.197 --> 23:55.835
but that must have been
really painful for you.

23:55.869 --> 23:57.904
So what made you
wanna be a therapist?

23:57.937 --> 23:59.339
Nice deflection!

23:59.372 --> 24:01.074
Now you're analyzing me.

24:01.107 --> 24:04.611
No, I'm not, I was
just wondering 'cause,

24:04.644 --> 24:06.746
I mean, I know it's
gotta be pretty hard.

24:06.780 --> 24:08.848
Well, I went through
a lot of shit,

24:08.882 --> 24:10.717
and I needed help,
but I got it,

24:10.750 --> 24:15.021
and then I realized
I wanted to help someone else.

24:15.055 --> 24:17.090
You know,
when people are in pain,

24:17.123 --> 24:19.626
they can't help but hurt others,

24:19.659 --> 24:22.896
and then the world sucks.

24:23.897 --> 24:25.265
Uh, I'm sorry.

24:25.298 --> 24:26.833
No, that's okay,
do you need to get it?

24:26.866 --> 24:29.235
Ugh, oh, no, it's just my job.

24:29.269 --> 24:31.137
On a Saturday night?

24:31.171 --> 24:32.705
Big meeting Tuesday.

24:32.739 --> 24:35.075
Big shot.

24:37.777 --> 24:39.212
We are so spoiled.

24:39.245 --> 24:41.781
Oh, yeah, it's a great time
to be a Boston fan.

24:41.815 --> 24:45.018
Just wish the Bruins
coulda pulled it off.

24:45.051 --> 24:47.253
Listen, I hate
to do this, but, um,

24:47.287 --> 24:50.256
I have a ton of work
to get through.

24:50.290 --> 24:52.892
Oh, oh, no problem.

24:52.926 --> 24:54.828
Um, before you go,
can I ask you something,

24:54.861 --> 24:58.965
and will you be honest with me?

24:58.998 --> 25:01.968
Um, okay?

25:04.337 --> 25:09.042
What were you doing
at the field today?

25:09.075 --> 25:11.077
What do you mean?

25:11.111 --> 25:14.314
I mean, I don't mean to
sound paranoid, it's just,

25:14.347 --> 25:17.383
it's a little weird, right?

25:17.417 --> 25:19.385
Yeah, weird, yes.

25:19.419 --> 25:21.254
I mean, I couldn't
believe it was you.

25:23.423 --> 25:27.193
Yeah, just
made me think of Joey.

25:29.729 --> 25:31.264
I don't know.

25:31.297 --> 25:34.000
You haven't spoken
to him, right?

25:34.033 --> 25:35.869
Not since we were kids.

25:38.104 --> 25:40.740
I mean, what happened?

25:40.773 --> 25:42.375
It's a long story.

25:42.408 --> 25:46.112
It's just messing
with me right now, it's... so.

25:48.481 --> 25:52.418
Pattie, I just wanted
to go by the ballpark.

25:52.452 --> 25:54.220
I played my last game there.

25:59.959 --> 26:02.028
I had a really great
time tonight, Pattie.

26:02.061 --> 26:04.063
Yeah, me too.

26:04.097 --> 26:06.833
Thanks for comin' over.

26:06.866 --> 26:08.434
You think I could
take you and JJ

26:08.468 --> 26:10.270
to a Sox game this weekend?

26:10.303 --> 26:12.071
That's very sweet
of you, but, um,

26:12.105 --> 26:14.174
I have a ton of work
to get through.

26:14.207 --> 26:16.409
Oh, right.

26:16.442 --> 26:18.745
Can't imagine
how hard you're workin'.

26:18.778 --> 26:19.812
Thank you.

26:19.846 --> 26:21.814
It's just that,

26:21.848 --> 26:25.451
you know, when you said JJ
was dyin' to go to a Sox game,

26:25.485 --> 26:29.289
I could really relate, you know?

26:29.322 --> 26:30.757
Listen, why don't you
come by tomorrow,

26:30.790 --> 26:33.426
and I'll take a break,
we can talk about it.

26:33.459 --> 26:37.163
Yeah?

26:37.197 --> 26:38.364
It's just that, you know,

26:38.398 --> 26:40.066
those tickets go really fast,

26:40.099 --> 26:43.336
and if you're gonna...

26:43.369 --> 26:45.271
Go spend some time
with your mom.

27:13.233 --> 27:14.434
Fuckin' Yankees.

27:46.165 --> 27:47.066
Hey, Denise,

27:47.100 --> 27:48.901
sorry I couldn't
answer the phone before.

27:48.935 --> 27:52.238
Don't worry about it,
did you listen to my voicemail?

27:52.272 --> 27:53.239
No, not yet.

27:53.273 --> 27:55.208
Richard needs
Gerton's Q-Two financials.

27:55.241 --> 27:57.277
Kellerman hit a wall.

27:57.310 --> 27:59.312
Well, then Susan has to get in
contact with Shanghai tonight

27:59.345 --> 28:00.947
and track 'em down.

28:00.980 --> 28:02.348
I'll ping her now.

28:02.382 --> 28:05.184
Okay, thanks, Denise.

28:19.899 --> 28:21.968
Hey!

28:22.001 --> 28:24.203
They're startin' some
no-name pitcher today.

28:24.237 --> 28:27.940
Yanks are gonna fuckin'
kill us again, bro.

28:27.974 --> 28:30.576
She loves red wine, huh?

28:30.611 --> 28:31.978
Oh, yeah.

28:32.011 --> 28:33.313
How'd your hot date go?

28:33.346 --> 28:35.014
Hysterical, Joey.

28:35.048 --> 28:36.115
You know I looked
like an idiot, right?

28:36.149 --> 28:37.016
- Did you?
- Yeah!

28:37.050 --> 28:37.917
I thought you were
gonna help me, man?

28:37.950 --> 28:40.119
Calm down, all right,
shit was funny.

28:40.153 --> 28:42.855
Yeah, you know you almost
ruined the whole plan, right?

28:42.889 --> 28:44.891
Really? That's not
a fuckin' plan.

28:44.924 --> 28:47.126
You want a plan? Go over
to Pattie's when she's out,

28:47.160 --> 28:49.228
get JJ, and bring him here.

28:49.262 --> 28:51.264
Kidnapping, that's a great plan.

28:51.297 --> 28:52.465
That's what I'd do.

28:52.498 --> 28:54.133
Yeah, I know.

28:57.403 --> 29:00.373
Fuckin' Sunday, and all that's
on is this bullshit, right?

29:00.406 --> 29:02.475
- Ugh.
- Ugh!

29:02.508 --> 29:05.912
- Ugh.
- Ugh!

29:05.945 --> 29:07.513
Ugh, do you think they
could hit the ball

29:07.547 --> 29:08.948
without screamin' like that?

29:08.981 --> 29:11.317
You wanna tell me
why she hates you?

29:11.351 --> 29:12.185
I don't know, Russo,

29:12.218 --> 29:14.921
I guess I was just
a shitty husband.

29:18.057 --> 29:19.592
You ever get violent with her?

29:24.597 --> 29:27.600
Is that what she told you?

29:27.634 --> 29:30.536
She didn't say anything.

29:30.570 --> 29:32.138
It's just she's got this
scar on her forehead...

29:32.171 --> 29:36.509
I never laid a hand on her,
Russo, I swear to God.

29:36.542 --> 29:40.146
I don't fuckin' do that shit.

29:40.179 --> 29:41.981
Okay.

29:42.014 --> 29:44.550
- Okay, I'm sorry.
- What the fuck, bro?

29:44.584 --> 29:47.987
- Whose side are you on here?
- I'm tryin' to help you out,

29:48.020 --> 29:49.489
but you're not exactly
makin' it easy, are you?

29:49.522 --> 29:51.658
Oh, I gave you the easy way.

29:51.692 --> 29:53.559
You're makin' it harder
than it has to be.

29:53.593 --> 29:55.261
Nah, that's ridiculous,
and you know it.

29:55.294 --> 29:56.697
What, should I get
locked up for 20 years?

29:56.730 --> 29:58.097
Is that what I should do?

29:58.131 --> 29:59.700
Nah, you should
get away with it.

29:59.733 --> 30:02.168
That can't happen, Joey, okay?

30:02.201 --> 30:03.670
All right, all right.

30:03.704 --> 30:06.506
Forget I asked.

30:06.539 --> 30:07.373
You wanna watch the game?

30:07.407 --> 30:08.975
Starts in about 20.

30:09.008 --> 30:12.245
Got a free bed.

30:12.278 --> 30:14.380
- Saddle up!
- Nah, I...

30:14.414 --> 30:16.115
got a lot of work to do, just...

30:16.149 --> 30:17.417
All right.

30:20.586 --> 30:24.257
Look, I think I can
get him to you.

30:24.290 --> 30:27.059
Yeah? What's the plan, boss?

30:27.093 --> 30:30.229
I wanna take him
to the game tomorrow.

30:30.263 --> 30:32.465
The Sox game?

30:32.498 --> 30:36.002
Yeah, I'm lookin'
at Monster seats.

30:36.035 --> 30:38.639
Fuck me.

30:38.672 --> 30:41.374
Wow, that sounds like
a nice family outing.

30:41.407 --> 30:43.042
Look, Joey, it's not like that.

30:43.075 --> 30:44.611
Fuck you, Russo!

30:44.645 --> 30:48.682
Seriously, man,
what the fuck are you doing?

30:48.715 --> 30:50.516
You gonna take her out,
you gonna be her best friend,

30:50.550 --> 30:52.418
and you're gonna
get in good with JJ?

30:52.452 --> 30:53.553
Good ol' Uncle Ronnie.

30:53.586 --> 30:56.489
How the fuck
does that help me, bro?

30:56.522 --> 30:58.257
You gotta at least
pretend that...

31:08.534 --> 31:10.737
Fuck you, I'm fine, thank you.

31:15.074 --> 31:16.175
Fuck.

31:18.679 --> 31:20.480
Bro, look,

31:20.513 --> 31:23.483
I gotta be a friend to her.

31:23.516 --> 31:26.586
Okay? I can't just
tell her what to do.

31:26.620 --> 31:29.623
I want you to
see your kid, Joey.

31:29.656 --> 31:32.358
Yeah, but when are you gonna
sack up and ask her?

31:32.391 --> 31:33.727
You know what, man,
fuck you, okay, Joey?

31:33.760 --> 31:36.028
I'm on it, all right?

31:36.062 --> 31:39.398
I got you, I promise.

31:39.432 --> 31:42.335
But you gotta let me
do it my way, okay?

31:42.368 --> 31:43.737
Or else, you know what,
you can get your sorry ass up

31:43.770 --> 31:46.205
and go get him
your goddamn self.

31:51.577 --> 31:54.681
Fuck yeah, now you're talkin'.

31:55.849 --> 31:58.351
Hey, I always wondered,

31:58.384 --> 32:01.053
how far'd you go?

32:01.087 --> 32:03.155
What do you mean?

32:03.189 --> 32:06.259
Baseball.

32:06.292 --> 32:08.227
You were really fuckin' good.

32:10.463 --> 32:12.833
Yeah, Joey, so were you.

32:15.636 --> 32:17.069
Here we go, Ronnie,
little base hit.

32:17.103 --> 32:19.272
Let's go, little Bingo.

32:19.305 --> 32:20.373
Here you go, Russo!

32:20.406 --> 32:22.074
No pitcher, no pitcher!

32:22.108 --> 32:24.377
Hit another dinger!

32:24.410 --> 32:26.546
Look at him, Russo,
he's scared of you.

32:26.579 --> 32:28.214
He's shakin'.

32:30.483 --> 32:31.852
Take your base!

32:31.885 --> 32:35.221
You're a pussy, Mahoney!

32:35.254 --> 32:36.122
Oh, yeah?

32:36.155 --> 32:37.256
See what happens
next time you're up.

32:37.290 --> 32:40.459
Cut it out, next pitcher
to hit someone is gone, got it?

32:40.493 --> 32:42.328
So he just gets away with it?

32:42.361 --> 32:46.432
Hey, you're three outs away
from somethin' special.

32:46.465 --> 32:47.734
Don't be dumb.

32:51.905 --> 32:53.439
Just two more outs.

32:53.472 --> 32:55.842
Here we go.

32:57.744 --> 32:59.846
Easy out, Joey.

33:09.388 --> 33:10.156
That's it!

33:10.189 --> 33:12.124
- You're outta here!
- Fuck you!

33:12.158 --> 33:13.727
Get outta here!

33:13.760 --> 33:14.728
Cute, real cute.

33:14.761 --> 33:17.463
- Fuck you.
- Get on the bench.

33:17.496 --> 33:19.599
Good game, good game, good game.

33:19.633 --> 33:22.703
Russo, that's the way you play.

33:22.736 --> 33:24.170
Great season, buddy.

33:24.203 --> 33:26.272
Good luck.

33:26.305 --> 33:27.874
What are you doing?

33:27.908 --> 33:29.643
No!

33:29.676 --> 33:31.177
Fuck outta here.

33:32.779 --> 33:36.282
Gonna fuckin' kill ya,
I swear to God!

33:36.315 --> 33:37.483
Why'd you do that?

33:37.516 --> 33:38.919
You coulda had a perfect game.

33:38.952 --> 33:40.887
A perfect game, dude.

33:40.921 --> 33:42.756
I got your back.

33:42.789 --> 33:44.357
Rozzie, kid.

34:19.324 --> 34:21.494
Hey, JJ!

34:21.527 --> 34:24.295
We, uh, haven't officially met.

34:24.330 --> 34:27.701
I'm Ronnie Russo,
friend of your mom's.

34:27.734 --> 34:28.567
I know.

34:28.601 --> 34:30.536
She's inside.

34:30.569 --> 34:32.271
Cool.

34:32.304 --> 34:33.406
Thanks.

34:35.676 --> 34:38.945
So, um, you're a big Sox fan?

34:38.978 --> 34:40.614
Me too.

34:40.647 --> 34:42.481
But you have New York plates.

34:45.317 --> 34:46.887
That's right.

34:46.920 --> 34:48.353
I just live in New York, though.

34:48.387 --> 34:49.723
I'm from Boston.

34:49.755 --> 34:51.456
Die-hard Sox fan.

34:54.493 --> 34:57.463
So, you think we're gonna
take it all this year, or what?

34:57.496 --> 35:01.233
Yeah, but we gotta
get better middle relief.

35:01.267 --> 35:03.436
We do cough up a lot of leads
in the sixth and the seventh.

35:03.469 --> 35:05.471
Exactly!

35:05.504 --> 35:07.506
You two talkin' politics?

35:07.540 --> 35:09.442
Ha-ha.

35:09.475 --> 35:11.812
- Ha-ha-ha.
- Hey, stop it!

35:11.845 --> 35:12.846
Never.

35:12.879 --> 35:15.816
So, I got us three tickets
for tomorrow at 1:00

35:15.849 --> 35:17.818
on the Green Monster.

35:17.851 --> 35:20.352
Really? We're going to the game?

35:20.386 --> 35:22.388
Thought we were gonna
talk about this?

35:22.421 --> 35:24.725
I'm sorry, I just got excited.

35:24.758 --> 35:26.893
I had to get the tickets last
night, or I was gonna lose 'em.

35:26.927 --> 35:28.695
But we can go, can't we, Mom?

35:28.729 --> 35:30.931
I have to work,
I've got clients.

35:30.964 --> 35:33.532
But I really wanna go!

35:33.566 --> 35:35.367
Uh, I screwed this up.

35:35.401 --> 35:37.470
I'm, I'm sorry.

35:37.503 --> 35:38.638
Can I go, Mom?

35:38.672 --> 35:40.674
Please?

35:40.707 --> 35:42.274
I could take him.

35:42.308 --> 35:45.645
It'd be my pleasure.

35:45.679 --> 35:47.279
I don't know.

35:47.313 --> 35:48.815
Or, you guys
can have the tickets.

35:48.849 --> 35:51.685
I just really want you
to be able to take him.

35:51.718 --> 35:52.819
It'd mean a lot to me.

35:52.853 --> 35:54.553
- I really have to work.
- Come on, Mom!

35:54.587 --> 35:56.388
It's the Yankees!

35:59.425 --> 36:00.927
You think you can handle him?

36:00.961 --> 36:03.395
Absolutely!

36:03.429 --> 36:04.330
Okay.

36:04.363 --> 36:06.432
Yes! I'm going
to the game tomorrow!

36:06.465 --> 36:08.601
Monster seats, baby!

36:08.635 --> 36:11.671
- Back before dinner!
- Okay!

36:11.705 --> 36:15.075
So what are you gonna do
with the other ticket?

36:15.108 --> 36:16.643
Sell it, I guess.

36:16.676 --> 36:17.677
Take your mom!

36:17.711 --> 36:20.914
Pay her back for
all the games she took you to.

36:20.947 --> 36:22.548
Oh, yeah.

36:22.581 --> 36:24.550
I mean, I doubt she can
make it thought.

36:24.583 --> 36:28.320
Ask her.

36:28.354 --> 36:30.957
I assume you don't
have any of your own?

36:30.991 --> 36:33.894
